similar can be used to detect the presence of the library.

    PKG_CHECK_MODULES([LIBDANE], [gnutls-dane >= 3.0.0])

    AC_SUBST([LIBDANE_CFLAGS])
    AC_SUBST([LIBDANE_LIBS])

